The growth respiration module has already been ported and committed (commit `6cce6c1`). The existing changes are only to `.ralph_last_output.log`, `.ralph_state`, and `PORTING_LOG.md` — these appear to be automation state files, not part of the port itself.

**Summary: Growth respiration port is complete.**

- **Source**: `src/biogeochem/growth_resp.jl` — faithfully translates `CNGRespMod.F90`
