  - All respiration factors preserved at 1.0 per Fortran
- **Tests**: `test/test_growth_resp.jl` — 5 test sets covering woody PFT, grass PFT, crop PFT, mask skipping, and zero-allocation cases
- **All 9068 tests pass**
